<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>BookSwap — your campus library, reimagined</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/app.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Hero + feature grid — scoped to the landing page. Uses design tokens
           from app.css so palette stays consistent. */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: var(--bs-bg);
        }
        .home-nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1.2rem 2.5rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bs-border);
            background: var(--bs-surface);
        }
        .home-nav__brand {
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: var(--bs-primary);
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .home-nav__links { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; align-items: center; }
        .home-nav__links a {
            color: var(--bs-text);
            padding: 0.45rem 0.9rem;
            border-radius: var(--bs-radius-md);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .home-nav__links a:hover { background: var(--bs-primary-light); color: var(--bs-primary); }
        .home-nav__cta {
            background: var(--bs-primary);
            color: #fff !important;
        }
        .home-nav__cta:hover { background: var(--bs-primary-hover) !important; color: #fff !important; }

        /* Hero */
        .hero {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 5rem 2rem 3rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero__pill {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.35rem 0.9rem;
            background: var(--bs-primary-light);
            color: var(--bs-primary);
            border-radius: var(--bs-radius-full);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.4rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -1.5px;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin: 0 0 1.2rem;
            color: var(--bs-text);
        }
        .hero h1 .accent { color: var(--bs-primary); }
        .hero p.lead {
            font-size: 1.15rem;
            color: var(--bs-text-muted);
            max-width: 620px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            line-height: 1.55;
        }
        .hero__actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        /* Feature cards */
        .features {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 4rem auto 0;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        .feature-card {
            background: var(--bs-surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--bs-border);
            border-radius: var(--bs-radius-lg);
            padding: 2rem 1.8rem;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: var(--bs-shadow-md);
        }
        .feature-card__icon {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            border-radius: var(--bs-radius-md);
            background: var(--bs-primary-light);
            color: var(--bs-primary);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .feature-card h3 {
            margin: 0 0 0.4rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--bs-text);
        }
        .feature-card p {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--bs-text-muted);
            font-size: 0.93rem;
            line-height: 1.55;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 6rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--bs-border);
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--bs-text-subtle);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="home-nav">
        <a class="home-nav__brand" href="/">📚 BookSwap</a>
        <div class="home-nav__links">
            <a href="/books">Books</a>
            <a href="/pdfs">Library</a>
            <a href="/curriculum">Curriculum</a>
            <% if (!currentUser) { %>
                <a href="/login">Login</a>
                <a class="home-nav__cta" href="/register">Sign up</a>
            <% } else { %>
                <a href="/profile"><%= currentUser.username %></a>
                <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <span class="hero__pill">🎓 IIT (ISM) Dhanbad — Peer-to-Peer Platform</span>
            <h1>Your campus library,<br><span class="accent">reimagined.</span></h1>
            <p class="lead">
                Borrow books from your classmates, share study notes, and let our AI map your lecture plan to exactly the chapters you need to read.
            </p>
            <div class="hero__actions">
                <a href="/books" class="bs-btn bs-btn--primary">Browse Books</a>
                <a href="/curriculum" class="bs-btn bs-btn--ghost">Upload Your Syllabus</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="features">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-card__icon">📖</div>
                <h3>Peer-to-Peer Lending</h3>
                <p>Find the book you need with a classmate who's already read it. Request, borrow, return — no bookstores involved.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-card__icon">📄</div>
                <h3>Shared Study Library</h3>
                <p>Notes, textbooks, previous year papers — all uploaded and searchable. Filter by department, course, or professor.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-card__icon">🎯</div>
                <h3>Curriculum → Chapter</h3>
                <p>Upload your lecture plan. We match each unit to the exact chapter in your professor's recommended book — with page numbers when we have them.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-card__icon">🤖</div>
                <h3>AI Librarian</h3>
                <p>Ask in plain English — "something gripping", "OS notes by second-years", "books Prof Sharma recommends" — the agent figures out the rest.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        BookSwap · MTech thesis project · IIT (ISM) Dhanbad
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
